urdu transliteration text:
ME BHI TO MATAMI HOON, ZAAKIR HOON SYEDA KANOHA PARHHA HAI MAIN NAY, HUMSHAKL-E-MUSTAFAA KAIS ZAKIRI KA MERI, QISMAT MEIN YEH SILA HOMARNE SAY PEHLAY YA RABB DEEDAAR-E-KARBALA HO
I HAVE RECITED EULOGIES ON HAZRAT ALI AKBAR as
@HujjatELC

YA RAB NAMAZE SHAB MEIN, BAS YEH DUA KARUN MEINKUCH DER USS ZAMEEN PAR, MAJLIS BAPA KARUN MEINHAR MATAMI KE LAB PAR, HAR DUM YEHI DUA HOMARNE SAY PEHLAY YA RABB DEEDAAR-E-KARBALA HO
EVERY MOURNER HAS THE SAME PRAYER AT ALL TIMES
@HujjatELC

HURR, AUN OR MUHAMMAD BESAR JAHAAN HUWE THEIANSARO AKRABA KI BIKHRE JAHAAN THEI LAASHEIPURSA WAHAAN MEIN DUNGA, GHAR ROOHE FATIMA HOMARNE SAY PEHLAY YA RABB DEEDAAR-E-KARBALA HO
HURR as, AUN as & MUHAMMAD as WERE BEHEADED,
@HujjatELC

SAJDA JHAAN KIYA THA, MAZLOOME KARBALA NEJHARA THA JUS ZAMEEN KO BAALON SE SAYYADA NEJAB MEIN WAHAAN PE JAAOON HONTO PE DUM RUKA HOMARNE SAY PEHLAY YA RABB DEEDAAR-E-KARBALA HO
THE LAND WHERE IMAM HUSSAIN as PROSTRATED,
@HujjatELC
